## Description {#details}

An <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/json/object">Object</a> is a JSON object, which maps strings to heterogenous JSON values.

It simulates <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/densemap">DenseMap&lt;ObjectKey, Value&gt;</a>. <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/json/objectkey">ObjectKey</a> is a maybe-owned string.

Definition at line 98 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/support/json-h">JSON.h</a>.
